         <h1 id="post-17">Call for Sponsors</h1>
<div id="print_icon">
</div>

<!-- <br clear="all" /> -->
<hr class="h2" />
          <div class="storycontent">
            <p>We are inviting sponsors to participate financially. If you are interested in supporting the DC-2008 Conference please take a look at our sponsoring incentives <a href="dateien/sponsoringoffers_DC-2008_V6.pdf">(pdf, english)</a>, <a href="dateien/Sponsoringangebote_DC-2008_V6.pdf">(pdf, german)</a> and <a href="http://dc2008.de/contact">contact</a> us.</p>
<p><strong>Printable Call for Sponsorship</strong> in <a href="dateien/sponsoringoffers_DC-2008_V6.pdf">English</a> and in <a href="dateien/Sponsoringangebote_DC-2008_V6.pdf">German</a></p>
<hr />
<h3>About the Conference</h3>
<p>In September 2008 the Eighth International Conference on Dublin Core and Metadata Application will be held for the first time in Germany. We are delighted to host this internationally renowned conference about innovative topics in digital information and Web technologies in Berlin.</p>
<p>The conference will focus on Semantic Web – the use of semantic &#8220;metadata&#8221; for the integrating knowledge sources, and Social Applications – the use of Web-based cooperation platforms such as wikis in managing metadata. These technologies flow together in applications such as Wikipedia, where structured information produced collectively can be integrated with other information sources.</p>
<p>Between 200 and 350 experts from science, business, and research from 30 nations visit the conference every year.</p>
<p>The annual conference takes place in a different country every year – most recently in Singapore, Mexico, Spain, and USA – and includes presentations of scientific papers, meetings of Dublin Core Metadata Initiative (DCMI) working groups and side events in the form of seminars and tutorials. <a href="http://www.dublincore.org">DCMI </a>is an organisation which develops global metadata standards, tools and infrastructures for the improvement of information management.</p>
<p>The conference will be held at the Humboldt-Universität zu Berlin.</p>
<hr />
<h3>Our Sponsoring Offers</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#S1">Our Offer</a></li>
<li><a href="#S2">Our Services</a></li>
<li><a href="#S3">Sponsor Rank</a></li>
<li><a href="#S11">Sponsoring Possibilities</a></li>
<li><a href="#S4">Survey of our Offers and Services</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="#S5">Sponsor Status: Main Sponsor</a></li>
<li><a href="#S6">Sponsor Status: Gold Sponsor</a></li>
<li><a href="#S7">Sponsor Status: Silver Sponsor</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="#S8">Additional Services</a></li>
<li><a href="#S10">Further Considerations</a></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p><a title="S1" name="S1" id="S1"></a></p>
<h3>Our Offer</h3>
<p>If you would like to present your company to a national and international<br />
clientele with worldwidely renowned experts of information technology, we<br />
can offer you the appropriate sponsoring cooperations.<br />
The International Conference on Dublin Core and Metadata Applications is<br />
a good place to present advertisement:</p>
<ul>
<li> The Dublin Core Conference is the largest international conference on metadata</li>
<li> Metadata plays a key role in the information age</li>
<li> Dublin Core is a well-established organisation with a good reputation</li>
<li> The Dublin Core Conference covers innovative and advanced topics of digital information processing such as Semantic Web and Social Computing</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p><a title="S2" name="S2" id="S2"></a></p>
<h3>Our Services</h3>
<p>Our services include</p>
<ul>
<li> your company logo on conference brochures and documents and advertising gifts</li>
<li> references to your company in announcements</li>
<li> advertising banners at the conference and/or at the locations for social events</li>
<li> product placement</li>
<li> display of brochures</li>
<li> company logo on the conference homepage</li>
<li> and much more!</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p><a title="S11" name="S11" id="S11"></a></p>
<h3>Sponsoring Possibilities</h3>
<p>In case you are not convinced about the optimal advertising effect of one of our ready made offers and services, we would be glad to offer you individually customised sponsoring cooperations.<br />
We would also be happy to negotiate individual conditions according to your budget together with you in a personal meeting, via e-mail or on the phone.</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S3" name="S3" id="S3"></a></p>
<h3>Sponsor Rank</h3>
<p>Our sponsoring offers are separated into the categories Silver Sponsor, Gold Sponsor and Main Sponsor. The sponsor status depends on the amount of money you support us with. You can accept our sponsoring offer with as little as 500.00 Euro.</p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/silver_sponsor_skal.png" alt="silver sponsor" title="Silver Sponsor" /></p>
<h4>Silver Sponsor</h4>
<p>Companies that accept our package offers with 500.00 to 1,000.00 Euro or support us with a contribution of 500.00 to 1,000.00 Euro will have the status of Silver Sponsor.</p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/gold_sponsor_skal.png" alt="gold sponsor" title="Gold Sponsor" /></p>
<h4>Gold Sponsor</h4>
<p>Companies that accept our package offers with 1,000.00 to 5,000.00 Euro or support us with a contribution of 1,000.00 to 5,000.00 Euros will have the status of Gold Sponsor.</p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/main_sponsor_skal.png" alt="main sponsor" title="Main Sponsor"/></p>
<h4>Main Sponsor</h4>
<p>Companies that accept our package offers with more than 5,000.00 Euros or support us with a contribution with more than 5,000.00 Euros will have the status of Main Sponsor.</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S4" name="S4" id="S4"></a></p>
<h3>Survey of our Offers and Services</h3>
<p>In the following tables you will find an overview of our sponsoring offers mentioning the associated services depending on the sponsoring status. A combination of our sponsoring offers is possible of course.</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S5" name="S5" id="S5"></a></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/main_sponsor_skal.png" alt="main sponsor" title="Main Sponsor"/></p>
<h4>Sponsor Status: Main Sponsor</h4>
<p>The Main Sponsor status is for companies who seize our offers with more than 5,000.00 Euro.</p>
<p><em>catering – conference dinner</em></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_2.2_skal.png" alt="conference dinner" title="conference dinner"/></p>
<p><em>catering – conference catering</em></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_4.1_skal.png" alt="conference catering" title="conference catering"/></p>
<h4>Consideration of the Offers for Main Sponsors</h4>
<p>The size of the displayed advertising banners depends on the special conditions of the conference venue and the conference reception venue. We are happy to offer you a product placement which is also dependent on the special conditions. Please confer with us about this issue. The mentioned prices are average prices that can vary according to your requests.</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S6" name="S6" id="S6"></a></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/gold_sponsor_skal.png" alt="gold sponsor" title="Gold Sponsor"/></p>
<h4>Sponsor Status: Gold Sponsor</h4>
<p>The Gold Sponsor status is for companies who seize our offers from 1,000.00 to 5,000.00 Euro.</p>
<p><em>catering – welcome reception</em></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_3.3_skal.gif" alt="welcome reception" title="welcome reception"/></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_5.3_skal.png" alt="USB-sticks" title="USB-sticks"/></p>
<h4>Consideration of the Offers for Gold Sponsors</h4>
<p>The mentioned prices are average prices that can vary according to your requests.<br />
In the case of promotional materials, you may make a donation towards the purchase of materials or provide support &#8220;in kind&#8221; (in which case your status as sponsor will depend on the value of the in-kind donation).<br />
We would be glad to put your donations in kind into our conference bag bringing Berlin closer to the participants (souvenirs).</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S7" name="S7" id="S7"></a></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/silver_sponsor_skal.png" alt="silver sponsor" title="Silver Sponsor"/></p>
<h4>Sponsor Status: Silver Sponsor</h4>
<p>The Silver Sponsor status is for companies who seize our offers from 500.00 to 1,000.00 Euro.</p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_11.2_skal.png" alt="name tags" title="name tags"/></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_9.2_skal.png" alt="ball pens" title="name pens"/></p>
<p><img src="dateien/Sponsoring_Images/Tabelle_10.1_skal.png" alt="post-it pads" title="name pads"/></p>
<h4>Consideration of the Offers for Silver Sponsors</h4>
<p>The mentioned prices are average prices that can vary according to your requests.<br />
In the case of promotional materials, you may make a donation towards the purchase of materials or provide support &#8220;in kind&#8221; (in which case your status as sponsor will depend on the value of the in-kind donation).<br />
We would be glad to put your donations in kind into our conference bag bringing Berlin closer to the participants (souvenirs).</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S8" name="S8" id="S8"></a></p>
<h3>Additional Services</h3>
<p>All sponsors will be presented with their company logo</p>
<ul>
<li>on our homepage</li>
<li>in our conference programme</li>
</ul>
<p>and, as far as possible, on the banners, mentioning their sponsor status.<br />
We ask for your appreciation that we cannot guarantee a complete listing of all sponsors in press releases and flyers according to the number of our sponsors. We reserve the right to favour the Main Sponsors being mentioned.</p>
<hr />
<p><a title="S10" name="S10" id="S10"></a></p>
<h3>Further Considerations</h3>
<p>The sponsor is responsible for the submission of printable company logos. In case you decide to make a sponsoring contract with us we provide you with the ready printed material for approval.</p>
